ss potential extensions and elaborations of the mesoatomic description\nof supramolecular soft matter network crystals, experimental observations of\nmalleable mesoatomic units in the precursor sponge phase as well as in ordered\ncubic networks, as well as possibilities for observing mesoatoms in primordial,\npre-crystalline states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Dec 2022 02:53:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-05"}
